<s> ANOQ, Congratz on your C++ DOM implementation.  </s>
<s> Actually the sentence reads: "Cloning any other type of node simply returns a copy of this node.  </s>
<s> " There is nothing about "without any data."  </s>
<s> When Comment, CDATASection, and Text nodes are cloned, their text contents are also copied for both deep and shallow cloneNode.  </s>
<s> Element.tagName is also cloned.  </s>
